title: Schubert - Symphony No. 8, Grand Duo - Abbado, COE
description:
Schubert: Symphony No. 8 and the "Grand Duo" in Cc major.

Schubert's Eight Symphony, the "Unfinished," and "Grand Duo" in C major, as recorded by Claudio Abbado and the Chamber Orchestra of Europe and released by DG in 1988. These are perfect interpretations and performances. As well, these recordings are the first based on the autograph manuscript.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
